### Test All DB Explorer Features
### Update these variables with your actual values

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7189
@connectionId = YOUR_CONNECTION_ID_HERE
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### PHASE 1: ER DIAGRAM
### ============================================

### 1. Get Graph Data (with columns)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/graph
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: nodes array with columns property populated
### Verify: Each node has columns array with name, type, isPrimaryKey, isForeignKey

### ============================================
### PHASE 2: QUERY SUGGESTIONS
### ============================================

### 2. Get Query Suggestions for a Table
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Categories/suggestions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: suggestions array with 5-7 queries
### Verify: Each suggestion has title, query, category, complexity

### ============================================
### PHASE 3: CHAT INTEGRATION
### ============================================

### 3. Get Tables List (for table name detection)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: tables array with tableName property
### Verify: Table names can be used for detection in chat

### ============================================
### PHASE 4: SCHEMA CHANGE DETECTION
### ============================================

### 4. Get Schema Changes
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/changes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Expected: hasChanges, newTables, deletedTables, modifiedTables
### Verify: Changes detected correctly, color coding works

### ============================================
### SUPPORTING ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 5. Get Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Table Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Health Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/health
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Sample Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/Categories/sample
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### CACHE MANAGEMENT
### ============================================

### 10. Clear Cache (if needed)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/cache
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Re-analyze Database
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/analyze?forceRefresh=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TEST SCENARIOS
### ============================================

### Scenario 1: First Time Analysis
# 1. Check status (should be hasData: false)
# 2. Run analyze
# 3. Check status again (should be hasData: true)
# 4. Get overview, tables, graph

### Scenario 2: Schema Change Detection
# 1. Get current schema (via analyze)
# 2. Make a schema change in database (add/remove table)
# 3. Get changes endpoint
# 4. Verify changes detected
# 5. Re-analyze to update cache

### Scenario 3: Query Suggestions
# 1. Get table detail
# 2. Get suggestions for that table
# 3. Verify suggestions are relevant
# 4. Test copy to clipboard in UI
# 5. Test execute in chat

### Scenario 4: Chat Integration
# 1. Navigate from DB Explorer to Chat (Query button)
# 2. Verify context message appears
# 3. AI responds with table names
# 4. Verify table names are clickable links
# 5. Click link to navigate back to DB Explorer

### ============================================
### PERFORMANCE TESTS
### ============================================

### Test 1: Large Database (100+ tables)
# Measure: Graph rendering time
# Expected: <2 seconds

### Test 2: Query Suggestions
# Measure: LLM response time
# Expected: <3 seconds

### Test 3: Schema Change Detection
# Measure: Comparison time
# Expected: <100ms (fingerprint check)

### ============================================
### ERROR SCENARIOS
### ============================================

### Error 1: Invalid Connection ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/invalid-id/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 404 Not Found

### Error 2: No Cached Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/changes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 404 with message "No cached schema available"

### Error 3: Invalid Table Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/db-explorer/{{connectionId}}/tables/InvalidTable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Expected: 404 Not Found

