### FRONTEND TESTING CHECKLIST
### ============================================

# Phase 1: ER Diagram
# [ ] Open DB Explorer
# [ ] Click "ER Diagram" tab
# [ ] Verify diagram renders
# [ ] Verify columns show in nodes
