# [ ] Test module filter
# [ ] Test click navigation
# [ ] Test zoom/pan

# Phase 2: Query Suggestions
# [ ] Select a table
# [ ] Click "Suggestions" tab
# [ ] Verify suggestions load
# [ ] Test copy button
