# Phase 3: Chat Integration
# [ ] Click "Query" button in table detail
# [ ] Verify navigation to chat
# [ ] Verify context message
# [ ] Click "Explain Relations" button
# [ ] Verify relationship context
# [ ] Click "Check Quality" button
# [ ] Verify quality context
